query:
UPDATE blocks
            SET kind = $1,
                sequence = $2,
                raw_content = $3,
                display_content = $4,
                derived_content = $5,
                last_actor_kind = $6,
                last_actor_id = $7,
                last_job_id = $8,
                last_workflow_id = $9,
                edit_event_id = $10,
                updated_at = $11
            WHERE id = $12
